<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is the daily CoxNet budget for papers of Saturday, July 4.
This budget will be updated at 6 p.m. EDT and afterwards as
necessary based on news developments.
</P>
<P>
   Questions about stories from Cox newspapers on this budget
should be directed to CoxNet, the Cox News Service, in Atlanta at
800-950-3739.
</P>
