<P>
   BRAVES-MAIN _ Coverage of today's Braves game. (Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA: 60 minutes after game's end.
</P>
<P>
   BRAVES-NOTEBOOK _ ATLANTA _ Inside the Braves' clubhouse.
