don't the afternoon thunderstorms develop like they should? Why
don't the tropical waves off the coast move to the west and drop
inches of rain on the state? What is the forecast for the next
week? If there's any hope of rain, when will it come and why then
and not now? (Mossman, Palm Beach Post)
