<P>
   BC-CNN-NERVE-GAS-NYT (moved on Thursday, July 2)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Thursday, July 2,
about the Cable News Network's retraction of a report that the
United States military used nerve gas in Laos in 1970 referred
incompletely in some copies to the managing editor of Time
magazine, which also used the report. He is Walter Isaacson.
</P>
