   BC-REPUBS-HISPANICS-NYT (moved on Wednesday, July 1)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Wednesday, July 1,
about Republicans who spoke before a national Hispanic organization
misstated the number of the California proposition in June that
called for abolishing bilingual education. It was 227. (Proposition
187 was a 1994 initiative to deny state services to illegal
immigrants.)
