<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-FLA-FIRES, which moved in ``a''
news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service  (lh) 
 
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I just figured with all these firefighters around these fires
couldn't get out of control. People don't realize how rural Florida
really is. They think beach, palm trees and bikinis.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Eddie Jensen, one of thousands of Floridians fleeing the fires
there.
</P>
